    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>A compounded method \u2013 exploiting the searching capabilities of an operation research algorithm and the power of bootstrap techniques \u2013 is presented. The resulting algorithm has been successfully tested to predict the turning point reached by the epidemic curve followed by the CoViD\u201319 virus in Italy. Futures lines of research, which include the generalization of the method to a broad set of distribution, will be finally given.</jats:p>",
